node.text: Our 2 hour season finale is on tonight at 8/9c!! Always a pleasure working with these guys and watching them do their thing - and getting to tell these important stories in the process. love you people. Cant wait for you guys to see this one ~ everyone loves cliffhangers, right? ♥️ @millionlittlethingsabc

node.text: #2021👩🏼‍🎓 !! lots of gratitude to those in my life that've helped and guided me through the years. and a massive shoutout to the teachers in CA, TX, and BC that've made my experience so much fun☺️tons of excitement for the next chapter in my life. long story short the mitochondria is the powerhouse of the cell. cheers
